            <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve">
            <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en"><p><note>Latin</note>: Emperor Caesar, son of deified Nerva, Nerva Trajan, Augustus, victor in Germania, 
               Chief Priest, <ref target="https://godot.date/id/JhByzVUCEkh7UhUPgkgFxi">holding tribunician power for the fourth time</ref>, 
               consul for the third time, father of the country, made the road using recruits raised in the province of Cyrenaica. </p>
            <p><note>Greek</note>: Emperor Caesar, [son of ] deified Nerva,[ Nerva Trajan], Augustus, [victor in Germania], 
               Chief [Priest . . .</p></div>
